LinkedHashMap<String, String> paltformVersions.= new LinkedHashMap<>();
for (Map.Entry<Platform, String> provided : inputVersions.entrySet()) {
    platformVersion.put(provided.getKey().name(), provided.getValue());
}

Then you could break the type dependency and just have String-to-String map on this API.

